data.description: Sellers are ready to pass this beautiful home on to it's next owners. This classic, well maintained has more than enough space to spread out and store all of your belongings.  The primary bedroom suite offers extra space, double vanity in the bathroom, soaker tub, walk-in shower, large closet with custom shelving and baskets.  Moving in to the primary bathrom, you will be offered a double vanity, large garden tub, and separate shower.  Venture upstairs to the other bedrooms with a "jack and jill" style bathroom situated between the second and third bedroom.  A large majority of the basement is already finished, adding even more room for everyone to spread out.  There's plenty of unfinished storage space left in the basement.  Spend some sunny days and warm evenings relaxing on the trex deck, and admiring the beautifully landscaped back yard.  Tankless water heater.  Washer and dryer to remain.
